To install, copy the files to the following locations:

Facepacks:
.../football manager 2009/data/sigfx/graphic/pictures/players/
Kits:
.../football manager 2009/data/sigfx/graphic/pictures/kits/
Logos:
.../football manager 2009/data/sigfx/graphic/pictures/logos/


Then go to the "Preferences" in your game. Then uncheck "Use Skin Cache" and check "Always Reload Skin On Confirm".

All credits go to the original creators of the facepacks, I only compiled this Superpack.
